.BG
.FN nwaylist.c0a
.TL
list from array, with appended 0
.CS
nwaylist.c0a(x)
.AG x
numeric array.
.RT
list with same dimensions as `x'.  Each element of the list is
constructed as `c(0,x[i])' for non-missing `x[i]', or as `numeric(0)'
for missing `x[i]'.
.EX
boxmat(nwaylist.c0a(data.matrix), boxf=boxplotm)
  # plot values of data.matrix
  # the height of each box is proportional to the numerical value
  # of the data in the corresponding cell of the matrix
.KW `boxmat', `boxplotm'.
.WR
